{"tid":737314,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［食鬼食評]—神級君御燒味","createTime":"2018-07-10T21:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T12:28:46.000Z","uid":182683,"like":21,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3e19f46099bd443f4f9b14711800b62b079693f5","tid":737314,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T21:15:16.000Z","msg":"今日係維園同樂仔x柏豪打藍球，好多囡囡圍觀大叫叫到我都肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  。聽講附近有間神級燒味，就睇下有幾把炮！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/050829_63fa1c36c07c8ed635a35c7180ee6824.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F050829_63fa1c36c07c8ed635a35c7180ee6824.png&h=1d17efe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一去到門口，full 曬，剩係見到廚房師傅係咁狂斬，d客粒聲唔出食到o習o習聲成隻豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我就知一定正到抽筋！<br />\n叫左個叉雞反，$32蚊？嘩！樂施會開嫁？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n叉燒，夠肥夠淋！d油香好癲！！最緊要係邊位夠燶仲要有少少脆，好野！切雞煮到岩岩好，滑到一放入口直接瀡走左。<br />\n份量睇相都知啦，$32蚊成個飯都係燒味，究竟間野賣到咁平係咩心態？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n我埋完單就走之前，見到張單$32蚊，忍唔到激動既心情，同斬緊既師傅講左句：燒你老尾！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （行內術語，意思係燒得好夠火候）師傅笑笑口：屌你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<br />\n君御燒味我一定翻o卓你！！！<br />\n評分：10/10<br />\n評語：好燒得！！！<br />\n<br />\nIg:hkfoodghost<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985d45f6a7893a45e9890ea8a24e051a1ca86b65","tid":737314,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T21:31:02.000Z","msg":"好足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfa615fb129c29627d303af68ac1df73cd2b7d6","tid":737314,"uid":193409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"係咪雞肶黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5bec237015239869722ca2cb90bc3979b1fb71","tid":737314,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebfa615fb129c29627d303af68ac1df73cd2b7d6","tid":737314,"uid":193409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"係咪雞肶黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:54:28.000Z","msg":"係 由於我叫左幾樣野都冇 佢益我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cea6d588c05508aff2e0f78ee38bedd7fd82eb","tid":737314,"uid":182683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"985d45f6a7893a45e9890ea8a24e051a1ca86b65","tid":737314,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T21:31:02.000Z","msg":"好足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多叉燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"$32真係好變態...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddb255a85aa58b0030eaa9a2bb2ec189a7bea48","tid":737314,"uid":134964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"呢間好嘢嚟，不過啲質素撞手神"},{"pid":"50775c2c973993ce536f70dfb7a1675f82415d28","tid":737314,"uid":32782,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾你講到唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cdb038494dca5fddc960dcef1f62a91b70d8b9","tid":737314,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddb255a85aa58b0030eaa9a2bb2ec189a7bea48","tid":737314,"uid":134964,"like":0,"disl